## 8. Launch Commands (✅ Working)
### Environment Activation
```bash
conda activate sovits_clean
```

### Start GPT-SoVITS API
```bash
cd /opt/conda/envs/sovits_clean/GPT-SoVITS
PYTHONPATH=/opt/conda/envs/sovits_clean/GPT-SoVITS python api_v2.py > ~/gpt_sovits_final.log 2>&1 &
```

### Start Bridge Service
```bash
cd /opt/conda/envs/sovits_clean/GPT-SoVITS
python sovits_bridge.py > ~/bridge_success.log 2>&1 &
```

### API Testing
```bash
# Check API status
curl http://127.0.0.1:9880/docs

# Check bridge status  
curl http://127.0.0.1:5000/
```

## 9. API Usage Examples
### OpenClaw Integration
```javascript
// TTS API call
const response = await fetch('http://127.0.0.1:5000/tts', {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
    body: JSON.stringify({
        text: "博士，今天也要加油哦！",
        voice: "guardian"
    })
});
const audioBlob = await response.blob();
```

### Direct GPT-SoVITS API
```bash
curl -X POST "http://127.0.0.1:9880/tts" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"text": "hello world", "text_lang": "zh", "prompt_lang": "zh"}'
```

